description: The ever-iconic Slyman’s Tavern, with its scrumptious food and chummy service, has integrated itself into the Cleveland experience since it first appeared over 50 years ago. Now the locals could not be more excited and delighted since Slyman’s is taking their tasty Tavern cuisine (including, of course, their famously huge Corned Beef sandwich) all throughout the streets!With a savory selection of sandwiches with tender meat piled as high as your anticipation for deliciousness, fresh hot juicy burgers, homestyle sides, and more, you gotta make your way to Slyman’s Food Truck (or invite them to come cater your next big party), for quality comfort cuisine that beyond satisfies.
name: Slyman's Tavern Food Truck
